==German==
===Noun===
'''Luft''' ''f'' (pl. ''Lüfte'')

# [[air]], [[atmosphere]]
# [[breeze]], [[zephyr]], [[breath]]

====Phrases====
* ''in die Luft fliegen'' - to be blown up
* ''in freier Luft'' - [[outdoors]], in open air
* ''an die Luft gehen'' - to go outside
* ''aus der Luft greifen'' - to [[fabricate]], [[invent]]

